                    <h3 class="text-md font-bold text-white mb-2">🔍 Sourcing Node Inspector</h3>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Click any asset inside the left-to-right network graph to parse sub-tier dependencies, risk scores, and alternative supplier playbooks.</p>
